<!-- Who We Are -->
<section class="section section-white">
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:start;">
    <div class="fade-up">
      <p class="eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3rem);margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Juba's Most <span>Trusted Cleaners</span></h2>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">City Cleaners South Sudan was founded in Juba with one simple mission: to give homes and businesses in South Sudan access to professional, reliable, and affordable cleaning services.</p>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">We recognised that South Sudan lacked a cleaning company that combined the professionalism of international standards with an understanding of the local environment. So we built one.</p>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.85;">Today we serve hundreds of homes, offices, NGOs and businesses across Juba — and we're growing every day. Our team is local, trained and deeply committed to delivering results that exceed your expectations.</p>
